      • toString

        public String toString()
        Returns a string representation of this queue. The string representation consists of a list of the queue's elements from the front of the queue to the back of the queue, enclosed in square brackets ("[]"). Adjacent elements are separated by the characters ", " (comma and space). Elements are converted to strings as by String.valueOf(Object).
